### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### ROLES
### Base: {{baseUrl}}/roles
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


### List ALL roles (across all accounts)
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles
Accept: application/json

> {%
  var roles = response.body;
  if (roles.length > 0) {
    client.global.set("roleId", roles[0].id);
    client.log("Captured roleId: " + roles[0].id);
  }
%}


###


### List roles for a specific account
# Requires accountId — run 01-accounts.http first to capture one
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles?accountId={{accountId}}
Accept: application/json


###


### Delete a role (admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{roleId}}
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}
